steps.name: Click on 'New Item' on the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click on the Configure button on side menu
Click on the 'Configure' Button on the Base Job Page
Select Boolean Parameter from drop-down menu
Input boolean parameter Pipeline Boolean Parameter
Set Some boolean parameters here as boolean parameter description
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Get name of the boolean parameter
